name: complex_1
comments: Interacts with contactin in cis form.

name: complex_2
comments: Heterodimer of CALCRL and RAMP3 (By similarity). Heterodimer of CALCRL and RAMP1 or CALCRL and RAMP2.

name: complex_3
comments: Heterotetramer of TRAP-alpha, TRAP-beta, TRAP-delta and TRAP-gamma. Interacts with palmitoylated calnexin (CALX)

name: complex_4
comments: Heterohexamer; TGFB1, TGFB2 and TGFB3 homodimeric ligands assemble a functional receptor composed of two TGFBR1 and TGFBR2 heterodimers to form a ligand-receptor heterohexamer.
